	[Grosse-Kunstleve, Acta Cryst. A55, 383-395 (1999)], which is
	implemented in lattice.c. bravais.{c,h}, bravais_virtual.{c,h} are
	removed.  spacegroup_type.{c,h} are moved to spacegroup.{c,h}.

